text: “læa thæcring rea di sng nuh pi yang prachachati khxng khea læw khea di klaw wa xo prachachati khxng chan cng khearph sakkara xallxh theid mimi phu di rab kar khearph sakkara dı «sahrab phwk than xik læw xun cak phraxngkh thæcring chan klaw kar lngthosʹ nı wan xan ying hıy ca prasb kæ phwk than”
